15.05.1967-19.2.2009
Principled, inspirational, funny, our rock, our lioness, she was my North, my South, my East, my West.
We will miss you beyond measure"░
ŁSir David Hardy
Chairman of Trustees 1995-2005
He would have been so proud that you chose to come here today
In support of Royal Museums Greenwich | rmg.co.uk/commemorate"║
